{"tid":2211464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（冷知識）上午10時05分是公司最常解僱員工的時間","createTime":"2020-09-21T06:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T15:15:36.000Z","uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c55ab2ac2335374d1b8f75633c924d306c50e6f0","tid":2211464,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:58:51.000Z","msg":"近日新冠肺炎疫情持續，很多公司為節流而宣布解僱員工。據非正式統計，如被解僱的員工，通常會在上午10時05分得知消息。<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼公司一般在上午10時05分解僱員工呢？因為上班時間通常在上午9時或之前，10時左右大部分員工已在公司。公司高層一般不是即日決定解僱員工，由於高層或老闆通常會稍晚一點回到公司，他們上班時隨即會把解僱信傳至人事部，此時已是10時左右。人事部員工一般會再用5分鐘把解僱信傳遞至被解僱的員工，加上公司要預留較充裕時間讓被解僱的員工執拾個人物品，即日內離開公司，所以10時05分是員工被解僱的「黃金時間」了。"},{"pid":"2565a54f16a4c1dd5c21afad50456b8d7bc5c70c","tid":2211464,"uid":217641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f39c8c8733c262f2c599361563dabb2ead939d67","tid":2211464,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829efd2098d6118cbe31f078c5df1733e75986d3","tid":2211464,"uid":53515,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"（冷知識）90%鬧鐘一般於早上06:00後響"},{"pid":"9f20d2541a14947fd5ace41ee98efbfd5b1918e8","tid":2211464,"uid":38352,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"你頭先10點05分比人炒左？"},{"pid":"c8b1452ede5f7702c97fb0da10cbb69fe4a177cf","tid":2211464,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:04:11.000Z","msg":"Noted with thanks"},{"pid":"250af895520531d100062ebff3cc1df50f19b261","tid":2211464,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f20d2541a14947fd5ace41ee98efbfd5b1918e8","tid":2211464,"uid":38352,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"你頭先10點05分比人炒左？"},"citedBy":0,"repl